  "texts": [
    "European Journal of Law and Economics (2024) 57:239-273 217).",
    "In the AI context, the burden of proof could be a hurdle to claimants.",
    "AI systems utilising deep learning or complex algorithms can be intricate and non-transparent in their decision-making processes.",
    "The inner workings of these systems can be difficult to comprehend or explain, making it challenging to identify and attribute specific defects or errors.",
    "When court decisions are uncertain, both producers and consumers may be inclined to adopt either excessive or insufficient levels of care."
  ]
}